    <ul>
      <li>1 kg main ingredient</li>
      <li>11/12 L superior spice</li>
      <li>2 Tbsp secret sauce</li>
      <li>1/4 C garnish</li>
      <li>A dash of seasoning</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Directions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Combine ingredients in a large bowl.</li>
      <li>Add seasoning and cook over low heat.</li>
